    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-6">Client Overview</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">A growing retail chain approached us with a key challenge: optimizing store operations, enhancing customer experience, and boosting sales by leveraging data insights. With our expertise in logistics, our team was eager to develop a robust solution tailored to their needs.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-6">The Challenge</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">The client faced difficulties in understanding foot traffic patterns within their stores. Traditional methods like manual counting and outdated surveillance systems proved inefficient, often leading to inaccurate data. Without a reliable solution to track customer movement, they struggled with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><span class="font-semibold">Inefficient staffing schedules</span> resulting in either overstaffing during quiet hours or understaffing during peak times.</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold">Missed sales opportunities</span> due to a lack of insights into high-traffic periods.</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold">Limited data</span> to inform store layout optimizations and marketing strategies.</li>
    </ul>
<h2 class="text-2xl mb-6">Our Solution</h2>
<p class="mb-6">Craftology developed an AI-powered people counting system designed to deliver precise data on customer movement and behavior. Our system uses state-of-the-art computer vision technology customized to align with our client’s specific needs.</p>
<p class="mb-6">System is deployed on premise to satisfy clients’ needs for compliance with local regulations.</p>
<h3 class="text-xl mb-4">Key features our solution includes:</h3>
<ul class="mb-6">
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Accurate People Counting:</span> Utilizing high-definition cameras combined with computer vision algorithms, our system accurately counts the number of visitors entering and exiting the store.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Heatmap Analysis:</span> Generates heatmaps that track customer movement, helping optimize store layouts by identifying high-traffic zones.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Peak Hour Identification:</span> Identifies peak shopping hours, empowering store managers to adjust staffing levels dynamically.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Data-Driven Decisions:</span> Seamlessly integrates with existing store management software, providing reports and dashboards for actionable insights.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="text-2xl mb-6">Implementation</h2>
<p class="mb-6">The project was executed in three phases:</p>
<ol class="mb-6">
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Assessment & Planning:</span> Conducted an initial audit of the client’s existing security hardware and requirements in order to plan store zones accordingly.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Installation & Integration:</span> Cameras were pointed strategically, and our vision software integrated on the client’s on premise server.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Optimization & Support:</span> Fine-tuning lead to improved accuracy based on real-world store conditions. We are ready to help the client any time in the future with troubleshooting and support.</li>
</ol>
<h2 class="text-2xl mb-6">Results</h2>
<p class="mb-6">Within three months of implementing the solution, the retailer experienced significant improvements:</p>
<ul class="mb-6">
