    <li><span class="font-semibold">Increased Sales:</span> Insights from heatmap analysis led to a 12% increase in sales through optimized product placements.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Improved Customer Experience:</span> Reduced wait times during busy hours, as staffing was aligned with actual foot traffic patterns.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Data-Driven Marketing:</span> Foot traffic data helped target promotions during high-traffic days, increasing campaign effectiveness.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Changed opening hours:</span> With insights from our outward facing camera, it turned out that many clients were coming to the store after closing hours. This way our client was provided with concrete evidence for further decision making.</li>
</ul>
